headline.print_headline: France Secures 1 Billion Euro Navy Deal in Egypt
headline.main: France Secures 1 Billion Euro Navy Deal in Egypt

lead_paragraph: France has secured its first major military contract in Egypt in about 20 years with a 1 billion euros (0.79 billion pounds) deal to sell four naval frigates, a French diplomatic source said on Saturday.
